                            </a>
                        <div class="project-description">
                            <div class="description-item">
                                <strong class="label">Description</strong>
                                <p class="content">
                                    Developed a RESTful Web API for managing a sports club system that allows users to register, view, and join services offered by coaches. The system handles memberships, payments, and service management with role-based access control for admins, coaches, and members. Implemented efficient data models, clean architecture, and secure authentication to ensure scalability and maintainability.
