                            </a>
                        <div class="project-description">
                            <div class="description-item">
                                <strong class="label">Description</strong>
                                <p class="content">
                                    Developed a scalable e-commerce application using a multi-layered architecture that separates Application, Domain, Infrastructure, and Host concerns. Implemented RESTful Web APIs to manage product catalogs, user accounts, and order processing. Applied SOLID principles, clean architecture, and efficient data modeling to ensure maintainability and extensibility. Managed data persistence with SQL Server and provided clear API documentation for testing and integration.
