                        <a href="https://github.com/Adel627/BookMate" target="_blank" class="stretched-link">
                            <h3>BookMate MVC </h3>
                            </a>
                        <div class="project-description">
                            <div class="description-item">
                                <strong class="label">Description</strong>
                                <p class="content">
                                    Developed a complete web application for managing books, authors, and categories using ASP.NET Core MVC. The system allows users to add, edit, and delete books, manage copies, and organize them by categories and authors. Implemented features such as image upload, pagination, and category filtering with a responsive Bootstrap-based interface. Designed the architecture following MVC principles to ensure scalability and maintainability.
